title: IAA Tonight | Recently Retired Shaquem Griffin Stops By AND Arizona Cardinals Preview
description: Former NFL player and University of Central Florida standout Shaquem Griffin has officially retired from the NFL is officially 'on to plan A.' Griffin had a chance to catch up with IAA Tonight and discuss what plan A is. Plus, we continue our Countdown to Kickoff with the Arizona Cardinals. What will it take for them to make a deep playoff run this upcoming season?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Shaquem Griffin, Leger Douzable, Omar KElly)
